<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA35">
<l>iṉiteṉpar kāma mataṉilu māṟṟa</l>
<l>viṉiteṉpar taṇṇīru mentā – yiṉiteṉṟu</l>
<l>kāmanīr vēḷātu niṉperumai vēṭparēṟ</l>
<l>cēmanī rākuñ ciṟitu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sweet, they say, is passion, and sweeter than that,</l>
<l>they say, is cool river water, o my father. If they,</l>
<l>without desiring passion [and] water as sweet, desire your greatness,</l>
<l>[your] protection has become [their] nature, a little bit.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
